Hungry for justice…and some free food? 😳

If the answer is YES, come join Tech + Social Impact’s Tech Talk where we’ll be talking about using technology to promote fairness and equity! We’ll also be giving away multiple Door Dash gift cards ($20 each)!  It’ll be on Wednesday, November 17th @ 7-8PM through zoom!!!!

Zoom Link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/93927736540?pwd=dk9FR25pbEVPakNGOEo4bGI4YWFBQT09

RSVP here: https://forms.gle/Y1rSXukRvpwb5TCF6


Come with your questions, and get ready to learn as our expert panelists will surely fascinate you with their cutting-edge research. We hope to see you there! 🙂
